                  </hi>. I took the prisoner—he told me he absconded be-cause he had lost a sovereign, and that he came back into the neighbourhood to be apprehended.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner</hi>. That is the truth—I lost part of the money—I brought back the horse and cart, and went away.</p>
